title: Match History
body:
When I click ANYTHING on the match history page it comes up with:


Error: 404
Player not found
The requested player was not found.

The requested player is me {{summoner:3}}

replies.body: I just tested mine and seems to be working. Have you tried restarting your client or even rebooting your machine?
What Horse said, I'm talking about the Match History page on the League Website
I don't think he's talking about the match history found within the client itself. How would you even get that error message within the client?
